BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Your health is your greatest asset—so how do some of our lead
 ers prioritize it while managing busy and demanding schedules?\n\nHave you
  ever wanted to hear their secrets to maintaining balance\, staying hydrat
 ed\, and prioritizing their health?\n\nJoin us for our Second Wellness Pan
 el: Health & Hydration\, where we’ll dive into one of the most fundament
 al aspects of wellness—hydration—and its powerful impact on performanc
 e and health.\n\nThis isn’t just a discussion about drinking more water\
 ; this is your chance to hear directly from selected leaders within our or
 ganization who will share their personal approaches to staying healthy and
  energized\, even during the most challenging days.\n\nEach of you is a va
 luable part of our culture\, and together\, we’re building a workplace w
 here everyone belongs. Let’s prioritize our well-being as a community an
 d continue creating a space that inspires and empowers us all.\n\nDon’t 
 miss the opportunity to uncover small\, simple habits that can have a big 
 impact on your well-being.\n\n\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - https://apexclearing
 .zoom.us/j/93455178751?from=addon\n\n
UID:040000008200E00074C5B7101A82E00800000000D54BE2894B97DB01000000000000000
 0100000000B3C7CE0BF849140BDE7CBB019783BF7
