BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Earth Day | Building a Sustainable Future\n\nEarth Day is a tim
 e to reflect on the steps we can take—big and small—to protect our pla
 net and build a more sustainable future.\n\nThis year\, we’re excited to
  partner with Moonshot\, our composting vendor for the Austin and Dallas o
 ffices\, to bring you a special Earth Day Composting Live Event. Check out
  our Impact Dashboard here.\nhttps://custom.moonshotcompost.com/apexfintec
 hsolutions\n\nEven if your office doesn’t compost\, this is an opportuni
 ty to come together\, learn\, and celebrate Earth Day as a company. Hosted
  live in Dallas and streamed for all offices\, this session will explore h
 ow collective action creates meaningful environmental impact.\n\nEach of y
 ou plays a vital role in shaping our workplace culture and amplifying our 
 efforts.\n\nBy celebrating Earth Day together\, we’re reminding ourselve
 s of the power of small\, thoughtful actions—actions that can grow into 
 a legacy we’re all proud of.\n\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - https://apexclea
 ring.zoom.us/j/95161662153\n\n
