BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we celebrate 13 incredible years of Apex!\n\nPlease 
 note: this Fireside Chat will be recorded and posted on The Lodge<https://
 thelodge.peak6.com/a/peak-6/home/ls/content/5664540914326519/fireside-chat
 -celebrating-13-years>.\n\nModerator Laura Agharkar\, VP of HR\, will lead
  a panel of our leaders—Bill Capuzzi\, Connor Coughlin\, Rajeev Khurana\
 , Terry Ray\, and Jessie Savu—in an inspiring conversation reflecting on
  the past year.\n\nTogether\, we’ll explore stories of collaboration\, r
 esilience\, and innovation that celebrate who we are as a team and inspire
  us as we continue to grow. This is our moment to honor how far we’ve co
 me and the incredible people behind the journey.\n\nLet’s come together 
 to celebrate us—the team raising the bar and shaping the future of Apex.
 \n\nAs a reminder\, please follow Zoom best practices: keep your camera on
  and stay muted unless speaking.\n\n---\n\n Apex Calendar SVCS is inviting
  you to a scheduled Zoom meeting.\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hos
 ts must use Zoom app or link to start this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.
 zoom.us/j/97690744799?from=addon\n\nOne tap mobile\n+13126266799\,\,976907
 44799# US (Chicago)\n+13092053325\,\,97690744799# US\n\nDial by your locat
