BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:BRIDGE | 4th Annual Urban Game Night\n\nJoin us for an exciting
  event of fun and games as we celebrate Juneteenth at BRIDGE's 4th Annual 
 Urban Game Night! This is a fantastic opportunity to unwind\, show off you
 r competitive spirit\, and connect in a low stakes\, high fun environment.
 \n\nDetails:\n✦ Date: Wednesday\, June 11\n✦ Time: Doors open at 3:45 
 PM CST\; Event starts at 4:00 PM CST\n✦ Location: Hybrid Event\nDallas: 
 14th floor Training Room\nZoom: https://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/99418161402
 ?from=addon\n\nDon't miss out on the fun – prepare to laugh\, play\, and
  maybe even brag a little! [:game_die:] [:space_invader:]\nLet’s make it
  a night to remember\, looking forward to seeing everyone there!\n
