DESCRIPTION:Zoom Link: https://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/4897488211\n\nThe Ape
 x Women's Network is delighted to invite you to a Zoom networking session 
 designed to help you practice your networking skills in a safe and support
 ive environment with colleagues from the US\, UK\, and the Philippines.\n\
 nDuring this session\, you'll be placed into breakout rooms for short\, in
 teractive conversations. It’s a fun and easy way to:\n\n  *\nStrengthen 
 the skills you learned during the workshop.\n  *\nGain confidence networki
 ng in small groups.\n  *\nBuild meaningful connections with colleagues acr
 oss Apex.\n\n\nCollaboration and teamwork are the lifeblood of our success
 \, and this is a great opportunity to continue your growth while fostering
  connections with your global colleagues.\n\nWe’re looking forward to se
 eing you and connecting during this exciting session!\n\nPlease note that 
 all Employee Resource Groups (ERGs) and events are open to everyone\, rega
 rdless of background\, and we encourage all employees to join any group. T
 his includes allies and employees who self-identify.\n
