BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:You are invited to participate in the annual Information Securi
 ty Technical Tabletop Exercise aimed at strengthening our organization's p
 reparedness against cyber threats and ensuring the robustness of our incid
 ent response procedures.\n\nDuring this exercise\, we encourage all partic
 ipants to approach this exercise with curiosity\, creativity\, and a willi
 ngness to embrace different viewpoints and unfamiliar approaches.  This ex
 ercise will provide a unique opportunity to bring together technical exper
 ts\, key stakeholders\, and incident response team members to engage in a 
 simulated cyber incident scenario\, working collaboratively to identify we
 aknesses\, analyze impacts\, and develop effective response strategies. Th
 is is a valuable opportunity to learn where we stand today as an organizat
 ion against emerging threats while enhancing technical response capabiliti
 es\, improve communication across teams\, and refine our cybersecurity pro
 tocols.\n\nWe look forward to your participation and insights in this crit
 ical exercise. The simulated scenario will be introduced on the day of the
  event during the exercise itself. Prior to the event day\, simulated role
 s be shared to confirm the Incident Response roles everyone will be fulfil
 ling.\n\nIf you have any questions or need additional information\, feel f
 ree to reach out to me directly.\n\n**Disclaimer**\nThe meeting will be re
 corded with Zoom AI Companion and automatically started at the beginning o
 f exercise.\n\nHector Peña is inviting you to a scheduled Zoom meeting.\n
 \nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hosts must use Zoom app or link to sta
 rt this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/93189705110?pwd=2qB3ESFK9
 wsw9SJdbTE8NMHDF22s9i.1&from=addon\n\nPassword: 118039\n\nOne tap mobile\n
