 ttps://jira.apexclearing.local/secure/RapidBoard.jspa?rapidView=51&quickFi
 lter=268&quickFilter=2204\n\nInstructions:\n\n  *   We will review cases t
 hat have the status “Ready for Prod Approval” (ATR/SYS) or “Ready fo
 r Approval” (TR).\n  *   Appropriate people should be there to present t
 heir case for approval.\n  *   Each case as a minimum should have the foll
 owing criteria to be considered:\n     *   Priority\n     *   Release Inst
 ructions\n     *   Verification Steps\n     *   Rollback Steps\n     *   R
 elease Date/Time\n     *   Risk\n     *   Tester\n     *   Code/ Peer Revi
 ew\n     *   UAT evidence\n  *   Any cases that are not represented or do 
 not meet the entrance criteria\, will be deferred to the US CAB.\n\n\nhttp
 s://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/91788322034?from=addon\n\n
