BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Join Apex Women’s Network for a candid and lively panel featu
 ring Apex parents Elise Luna\, Andrew Glenn\, Sonia Singh\, and Mitchell M
 cComb\, each bringing unique perspectives from different stages of parenth
 ood. Hear real stories\, practical advice\, and insights about Apex's perk
 s\, along with a few laughs about balancing work\, family\, and everything
  in between.\n\nWhether you have kids\, are thinking about it\, or simply 
 want to support your colleagues\, all are welcome! Bring your questions\, 
 curiosity\, and sense of humor!\n\nPlease note that all Employee Resource 
 Groups (ERGs) and events are open to everyone\, regardless of background\,
  and we encourage all employees to join any group. This includes allies an
 d employees who self-identify.\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hosts 
 must use Zoom app or link to start this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.zoo
 m.us/j/99381099253?from=addon\n\nThank you\,\nApex Women’s Network\n\n
