BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Just adding a meeting to discuss https://apexclearing.atlassian
 .net/browse/OB-1113\n\nWe’ve encountered a recurring issue while debuggi
 ng requests that traverse Cloud Armor. During incident investigation\, we 
 found it difficult to correlate Cloud Armor-related log entries with speci
 fic request traces in Datadog. This made it challenging to pinpoint the so
 urce of issues and increased time to resolution.\nCurrent Situation:\n- We
  use Datadog’s tracing to connect all components of a request via trace_
 id.\n- Cloud Armor logs (enforcedSecurityPolicy field in GLB logs) do not 
 natively include the trace_id from the request path.\n- Some Cloud Armor l
 ogs do include a field like data.trace:projects/[project]/traces/[trace_id
 ]\, but Datadog does not automatically recognize [trace_id] for https://do
 cs.datadoghq.com/tracing/other_telemetry/connect_logs_and_traces/ log-trac
 e correlation.\n- As a workaround\, we had to manually trace and ask vario
 us teams for logs\, which is not scalable.\nImpact:\n- Manual correlation 
 between logs and traces is slow\, especially during incident response.\n- 
 Not having log-trace correlation for Cloud Armor logs limits our ability t
 o quickly debug security-related issues.\n\n\n\n Gary Armstrong is invitin
 g you to a scheduled Zoom meeting.\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note ho
 sts must use Zoom app or link to start this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing
 .zoom.us/j/92299040538?from=addon\n\nOne tap mobile\n+13092053325\,\,92299
 040538# US\n+13126266799\,\,92299040538# US (Chicago)\n\nDial by your loca
 tion\n+1 309 205 3325 US\n+1 312 626 6799 US (Chicago)\n+1 346 248 7799 US
  (Houston)\n+1 360 209 5623 US\n+1 386 347 5053 US\n+1 507 473 4847 US\n+1
  564 217 2000 US\n+1 646 876 9923 US (New York)\n+1 646 931 3860 US\n+1 66
 9 444 9171 US\n+1 669 900 6833 US (San Jose)\n+1 689 278 1000 US\n+1 719 3
 59 4580 US\n+1 253 205 0468 US\n+1 253 215 8782 US (Tacoma)\n+1 301 715 85
 92 US (Washington DC)\n+1 305 224 1968 US\nMeeting ID: 922 9904 0538\nFind
  your local number: https://apexclearing.zoom.us/u/aqMOpcq54\n\nJoin by SI
 P\n92299040538@zoomcrc.com\n\nJoin by H.323\n144.195.19.161 (US West)\n206
 .247.11.121 (US East)\n115.114.131.7 (India Mumbai)\n115.114.115.7 (India 
 Hyderabad)\n159.124.15.191 (Amsterdam Netherlands)\n159.124.47.249 (German
 y)\n159.124.104.213 (Australia Sydney)\n159.124.74.212 (Australia Melbourn
