DESCRIPTION:Let’s kick off GREAT at Apex\nJoin Bill and Laura — with Co
 nnor\, Daniel\, Lucille\, Andrew\, and Rajeev — to launch the five behav
 iors that’ll level us up: Grit\, Results\, Empathy\, Accountability\, Te
 amwork (GREAT).\nWhy join?\n\n  *   Less guessing\, faster wins\, more tru
 st\n  *   Hear why now\, what “good” actually looks like here\, and ho
 w we’ll back you up\n\nWhat you’ll get\n\n  *\nClear expectations\n  *
    Simple tools to lean into each behavior\n  *   Real stories where GREAT
  changed the outcome\n  *   Straight-up Q&A\n\nWhat changes after\n\n  *  
  A shared way to talk about how we work\n  *   Clear standards we’ll all
  hold ourselves to\n\nBring your team and your questions — and let’s m
 ake GREAT our default.\nAs a reminder\, please follow Zoom best practices:
  keep your camera on and stay muted unless speaking.\n\n__________________
