DESCRIPTION:Apex Women’s Network invites you to an interactive Confident 
 Communication Workshop with Louise Keenan Clarke\, an expert communication
  coach with 25 years of experience in empowering professionals to communic
 ate with confidence and impact.\n\nReady to elevate your communication pre
 sence? In this hands-on session\, you’ll:\n\n  *   Unlock strategies for
  assertive\, confident communication\n  *   Master powerful self-introduct
 ions and pitching\n  *   Learn to speak with clarity and impact\n  *   Har
 ness storytelling for stronger business influence\n  *   Practice with rea
 l-life examples and leave with actionable steps to elevate your presence\n
 \nEveryone is welcome! Join us to build communication skills that will acc
 elerate your career and amplify your impact. Please note that we will hold
  a separate live session for the Philippines office on Monday\, 11/17. Be 
 on the lookout for an invitation.\nPlease note that all Employee Resource 
 Groups (ERGs) and events are open to everyone\, regardless of background\,
  and we encourage all employees to join any group. This includes allies an
 d employees who self-identify.\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hosts 
 must use Zoom app or link to start this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.zoo
 m.us/j/91865113362?from=addon\n\nThank you\,\nApex Women’s Network\n\n
