 Trevor Vernier (Director of Risk) explains how Apex handles option exercis
 es and assignments—covering calls vs. puts\, pin risk\, seller exposure\
 , OCC/DTC capital requirements—and previews the shift to Ascend for real
 -time processing and tighter risk control.\n  *\n\n  *\nLive Q&A with Trev
 or Vernier (15 mins) Got questions? Trevor will be here to answer them liv
 e! Curious minds are extra welcome.\n  *\n\n\n[:gift:] Bonus:\nEarn Lesson
 ly credit for attending this episode! Level up your knowledge AND your cou
 rse progress. Earn prizes live in the session!\n\nZOOM LINK HERE<https://a
 pexclearing.zoom.us/j/7711412078>\n\nSee you there!\n-Your Learning & Orga
 nizational Development Team\n\n
