DESCRIPTION:\nThis interactive session\, lasting 45-60 minutes\, is specifi
 cally tailored to address the nutritional challenges faced by busy profess
 ionals. It will cover essential topics such as building balanced meals and
  snacks\, convenient breakfast and lunch solutions\, healthy on-the-go opt
 ions\, and guidance on weekly food staples. Participants will also gain sc
 ience-backed insights into supplements and practical tips for optimising n
 utrition.\n\n\nAn interactive overnight oats session will also be included
 \, giving hints and tips on preparation.\n\nThe workshop provider\, Cather
 ine Downey is a registered NHS dietician with many years of experience.\n\
