 ne.\n\n________________________________\nFrom: Alexandra (Sasha) Shuman-St
 rohman <ashumanstrohman@apexfintechsolutions.com>\nSent: 21 October 2025 1
 5:49:08 (UTC+00:00) Dublin\, Edinburgh\, Lisbon\, London\nTo: Alexandra (S
 asha) Shuman-Strohman <ashumanstrohman@apexfintechsolutions.com>\nCc: mani
 la <manila@apexfintechsolutions.com>\; Lisa Stevenson <lstevenson@apexfint
 echsolutions.com>\nSubject: Apex Women’s Network | Confident Communicati
 on Workshop\nWhen: 17 November 2025 08:30-09:30.\nWhere: https://apexclear
 ing.zoom.us/j/98907334982?from=addon\n\n\nApex Women’s Network invites y
 ou to an interactive Confident Communication Workshop with Louise Keenan C
 larke\, an expert communication coach with 25 years of experience in empow
 ering professionals to communicate with confidence and impact.\n\nReady to
  elevate your communication presence? In this hands-on session\, you’ll:
 \n\n  *   Unlock strategies for assertive\, confident communication\n  *  
  Master powerful self-introductions and pitching\n  *   Learn to speak wit
 h clarity and impact\n  *   Harness storytelling for stronger business inf
 luence\n  *   Practice with real-life examples and leave with actionable s
 teps to elevate your presence\n\nEveryone is welcome! Join us to build com
 munication skills that will accelerate your career and amplify your impact
 .\nPlease note that all Employee Resource Groups (ERGs) and events are ope
 n to everyone\, regardless of background\, and we encourage all employees 
 to join any group. This includes allies and employees who self-identify.\n
 \nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hosts must use Zoom app or link to sta
 rt this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/98907334982?from=addon\n\
 nThank you\,\nApex Women’s Network\n\n
