BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION: The Apex Women's Network is delighted to invite you to our fin
 al Zoom networking session of the year!\n\n\n\nBuilding on the success of 
 our previous sessions\, which have helped participants strengthen their ne
 tworking skills and foster meaningful connections\, this event promises to
  be another valuable opportunity to connect with colleagues from the US\, 
 UK\, and the Philippines in a safe and supportive environment.\n\n\n\nDuri
 ng this session\, you'll be placed into breakout rooms for short\, interac
 tive conversations. It’s a fun and effective way to:\n\n  *   Reinforce 
 the skills you learned during the workshop.\n\n  *   Gain confidence in ne
 tworking in small groups.\n\n  *   Build meaningful connections with colle
 agues across Apex.\n\n\n\nCollaboration and teamwork are the lifeblood of 
 our success\, and this final session is a great opportunity to continue yo
 ur growth while celebrating the connections you’ve built throughout the 
 year. We’re excited to see you and wrap up the year with this engaging a
 nd impactful event!\n\n\nPlease note that all Employee Resource Groups (ER
 Gs) and events are open to everyone\, regardless of background\, and we en
 courage all employees to join any group. This includes allies and employee
 s who self-identify.\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hosts must use Z
 oom app or link to start this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/525
 7846519\n\nThank you\,\nApex Women’s Network\n\n
