BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Hey Apex Team!\nJoin us for a special “Watch Live and Q&A” 
 event brought to you by Learning & Development! Lunch and snacks will be p
 rovided at your respective locations.\n\n[:sparkles:] What’s Happening? 
  [:sparkles:]\n\n  *\nWatch Inside Apex Podcast – Episode 16: “ACATs a
 nd Corporate Actions” (26 mins). Dive into the world where Logan Jones\,
  Senior Manager\, Operations explains how Apex handles ACATS in-kind trans
 fers\, combats synthetic account fraud through industry collaboration and 
 client education\, and mitigates the high-stakes risks of corporate action
 s.\n  *\n\n  *\nLive Q&A with Logan Jones - Got questions? Logan will be h
 ere to answer them live! Curious minds are extra welcome. Let’s spark gr
 eat conversations!\n\nLocation:\nAustin - Ladybird\nBelfast - Donard (12pm
  local time)\nChicago - [UPDATED] Chicago (on 2nd floor)\nDallas - Trainin
 g rooms A&B\nManila - Siargao (12pm local time)\nNew York - Boardroom\nPor
 tland - Mount Hood\n\nFood is available on a first come first served basis
 .\n\n  *\n\n\n[:gift:] Bonus:\nPlease make sure to sign in to receive Less
 only credit for attending this episode! Level up your knowledge AND your c
 ourse progress. Earn prizes live in the session!\n\nZOOM LINK HERE<https:/
