BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:The Apex Women's Network is delighted to invite you to our fina
 l Zoom networking session of the year!\n\n\n\nBuilding on the success of o
 ur previous sessions\, which have helped participants strengthen their net
 working skills and foster meaningful connections\, this event promises to 
 be another valuable opportunity to connect with colleagues from the US\, U
 K\, and the Philippines in a safe and supportive environment.\n\n\n\nDurin
 g this session\, you'll be placed into breakout rooms for short\, interact
 ive conversations. It’s a fun and effective way to:\n\n  *   Reinforce t
 he skills you learned during the workshop.\n\n  *   Gain confidence in net
 working in small groups.\n\n  *   Build meaningful connections with collea
 gues across Apex.\n\n\n\nCollaboration and teamwork are the lifeblood of o
 ur success\, and this final session is a great opportunity to continue you
 r growth while celebrating the connections you’ve built throughout the y
 ear. We’re excited to see you and wrap up the year with this engaging an
 d impactful event!\n\n\nPlease note that all Employee Resource Groups (ERG
 s) and events are open to everyone\, regardless of background\, and we enc
 ourage all employees to join any group. This includes allies and employees
  who self-identify.\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hosts must use Zo
 om app or link to start this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/7579
 091646\n\nThank you\,\nApex Women’s Network\n\n\n\n
