DESCRIPTION:Hey Apex Team!\nGrab your snacks and join us for a special “W
 atch Live” event brought to you by Learning & Development!\n\n[:sparkles
 :] What’s Happening?\n\n  *\nWatch Inside Apex Podcast – Episode 17: 
 “Cost Basis\, Tax Reporting and Tax Advantaged Accounts” with Patti Ne
 il (15 mins) Let's get into the complexities of cost basis and tax operati
 ons within the financial services industry\, where Bill Brennan and Patti 
 Neil explore how accurate tax reporting\, intricate cost basis calculation
 s\, and advanced technology work together to manage vast amounts of data.\
 n  *\n\n  *\nLive Q&A with Patti (15 mins) Got questions? Patti will be he
 re virtually to answer them live! Curious minds are extra welcome.\n  *\n\
 n\n[:gift:] Bonus:\nEarn Lessonly credit for attending this episode! Level
  up your knowledge AND your course progress. Earn prizes live in the sessi
 on!\n\nZOOM LINK HERE<https://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/7711412078>\n\nSee yo
 u there!\n-Your Learning & Organizational Development Team\n\n
