DESCRIPTION:Hey Apex Team!\nGrab your snacks and join us for a special “W
 atch Live” event brought to you by Learning & Development!\n\n[:sparkles
 :] What’s Happening?\n\n  *\nWatch Inside Apex Podcast – Episode 18: 
 “Margins” with Joe Lucas. Join us as we dive deep into the high-stakes
  world of margin operations\, where Bill Brennan and Joe Lucas unpack the 
 intricate dance between regulatory compliance and financial risk that gove
 rns billions in leveraged positions. Discover how cutting-edge technology 
 and rigorous oversight balance powerful trading opportunities with protect
 ion against catastrophic financial exposure.\n  *\n\n  *\nLive Q&A with Jo
 e (15 mins) Got questions? Joe will be here virtually to answer them live 
 from the Dallas office! If you are in the Dallas office\, please stop by t
 he training rooms. Curious minds are extra welcome.\n  *\n\n\n[:gift:] Bon
 us:\nEarn Lessonly credit for attending this episode! Level up your knowle
 dge AND your course progress. Earn prizes live in the session!\n\nZOOM LIN
 K HERE<https://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/7711412078>\n\nSee you there!\n-Your
  Learning & Organizational Development Team\n\n\n
