BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Hi Team\,\nBuilding an idea for a monthly retrospective\, I wan
 t to refine the focus to better connect our daily work with our long-term 
 growth.\nTo make our time together even more focused and productive\, I'd 
 like to propose a small adjustment.\nThis is not meant to be another statu
 s meeting or a re-hash of our sprint reviews. The goal is to take a step b
 ack from the day-to-day tickets and stand-ups to see the bigger picture.\n
 Touching on key accomplishments and challenges from the past month's sprin
 ts\, but the real focus will be on what we learned from that work and how 
 we can apply it.\nThis process helps us connect the dots between our tasks
  and our skills\, ensuring that we are all growing while we deliver value.
 \nI've updated the short questionnaire. Please take a few minutes to fill 
 it out.\nMonthly Security Impact & Growth: 2026 – Fill out form<https://
 forms.office.com/r/V9RWXGBTV4>\n\nRegards\,\nSwapnil Pawar\n
UID:040000008200E00074C5B7101A82E00800000000F27D94C9674FDC01000000000000000
