  Bethany Christian\, Mgr\, Treasury & Spencer Maldonado\, Dir\, Treasury.\
 nHere is what to expect:\nDive into the vital world of cash flow managemen
 t\, where Bill explores the treasury vault with two unsung heroes who cont
 rol the flows\, Bethany Christian and Spencer Maldonado. Discover how they
  navigate nearly a billion dollars daily through complex operations includ
 ing DTC settlement\, NSCC requirements\, OCC collateral management\, and s
 trategic cash investments.\nLive Q&A with Bethany & Spencer (15 mins) Got 
 questions about cash management\, treasury operations\, or investment stra
 tegies? Bethany and Spencer will be here virtually to answer them live! ZO
 OM LINK<https://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/93130972230?from=addon>\nBonus: Ear
 n Lessonly credit for attending this episode! Level up your knowledge AND 
 your course progress. Participate in our live poll to win prizes including
  a Bluetooth speaker and Apex caps!\n🥪Catering will be provided first c
 ome first serve and in the following conference rooms🥟:\nAustin: 4th fl
 oor\nChicago: Chicago room\nPortland: Mt Hood\nDallas: Training Room A&B\n
 New York: Chrysler-A\nBelfast: Donard\n\n\n
