BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:The Apex Women's Network is excited to invite you to our first 
 Zoom networking session of the year!\n\nBuilding on the success of our pre
 vious sessions\, which have helped participants strengthen their networkin
 g skills and foster meaningful connections\, this event promises to be ano
 ther valuable opportunity to connect with colleagues from the US\, UK\, an
 d the Philippines in a safe and supportive environment.\n\n\n\nDuring this
  session\, you'll be placed into breakout rooms for short\, interactive co
 nversations. It’s a fun and effective way to:\n\n  *   Reinforce the ski
 lls you learned during the workshop.\n\n  *   Gain confidence in networkin
 g in small groups.\n\n  *   Build meaningful connections with colleagues a
 cross Apex.\n\n\n\nCollaboration and teamwork are the lifeblood of our suc
 cess\, and this final session is a great opportunity to continue your grow
 th while celebrating the connections you’ve built throughout the year. W
 e’re excited to see you and start the year with this engaging and impact
 ful event!\n\n\nPlease note that all Employee Resource Groups (ERGs) and e
 vents are open to everyone\, regardless of background\, and we encourage a
 ll employees to join any group. This includes allies and employees who sel
 f-identify.\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hosts must use Zoom app o
 r link to start this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/5176269351\n
 \nThank you\,\nApex Women’s Network\n\n
