DESCRIPTION:PEAK6 Firmwide All Hands Meeting\nIn January\, we held a firmwi
 de All Hands focused on AI usage and the high-impact AI innovation happeni
 ng across the firm. Now\, you’re invited to join us February 25 from 3:3
 0 - 4:45 p.m. CT for anothe\n\n\nIn January\, we held a firmwide All Hands
  focused on AI usage and the high-impact AI innovation happening across th
 e firm. Now\, you’re invited to join us February 25 from 3:30 - 4:45 p.m
 . CT for another firmwide All Hands\, during which leaders from each PEAK6
  line of business\, as well as Matt and Jenny\, will fill us in on what th
 eir teams are working on now\, and how they plan to shape tomorrow.\n\nA r
 ecording of this meeting will be posted on the Lodge for those unable to a
 ttend due to their team’s schedule or other conflict.\n\nHow to RSVP and
  Attend:\n\n  *   In Office: Accept this calendar invitation and join team
  members in your office’s meeting location.\n\n  *   Virtual: If joining
  virtually\, accept this calendar invitation and use this Zoom link to joi
