 ATRIOT Act\, privacy/ID-theft\, KYC\, and AML\, including ACH fraud detect
 ion and post-trade surveillance across asset classes (insider trading\, sp
 oofing/layering\, ramping\, cross/wash trades).\nLive Q&A with Andrew & Ju
 stin (15 mins) Got questions about compliance culture\, regulators\, CIP/K
 YC/AML\, fraud prevention\, or trade surveillance? Andrew and Justin will 
 be here virtually to answer them live! ZOOM LINK<https://apexclearing.zoom
 .us/j/93130972230?from=addon>\nBonus: Earn Lessonly credit for attending t
 his episode! Level up your knowledge AND your course progress.\n🥪Cateri
 ng will be provided first come first serve and in the following conference
  rooms🥟:\nAustin: Bowling-Alley\nChicago: Kyroom & Chicago\nPortland: M
 t Hood\nDallas: Downtown (boardroom)\nNew York: Chrysler-A\nBelfast: Donar
 d\n\n\n
