DESCRIPTION:\nZoom Meeting Link: https://apexclearing.zoom.us/j/94498064754
 ?from=addon\n\nMeeting ID: 944 9806 4754\n\n______________________________
 ______\n\n\nOverview\n\nWeekly Operational Health Review (OHR) focused on 
 operational excellence\, system reliability\, and continuous improvement a
 cross the technology and operations organization. Each week we review serv
 ice health\, vulnerability posture\, critical incidents\, and post-mortem 
 action items to drive preventive action and improve the client experience.
 \n\nMeeting Sections\n\n  *   Service Health Review\n  *   Vulnerability H
 ealth Review\n  *   Incident Review\n  *   Post Mortem Action Items\n\nGoa
 ls\n\nReduce incidents & time to resolution by\n\n  *   Equipping service 
 teams to report on health status immediately\n  *   Identifying SLO/SLA ga
 ps\n  *   Reducing operational toil\n  *   Identifying technical challenge
 s impacting service levels\n\n…to improve upon the overall product exper
 ience for our clients.\n\n\nOverview and Format<https://apexclearing.atlas
 sian.net/wiki/x/BAC6hgE>\n\nAgendas<https://apexclearing.atlassian.net/wik
 i/x/ZQI9egE>\n\nMinutes <https://apexclearing.atlassian.net/wiki/x/gAAfjQE
 >\n\nParticipant Expectations: <https://apexclearing.atlassian.net/wiki/sp
 aces/Techcellen/pages/6555303940/Operational+Op+Health+Meeting+-+Format+an
 d+Overview#%5BmediaInline%5D-Routine-for-Accountable-Pairs>\n\nService Own
 ing Pairs — Engineering Managers and Product Managers who own services 
 — are the primary audience. As an owner of a product\, service\, or infr
 astructure you must be present or have a representative attend. Full detai
 ls<https://apexclearing.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/Techcellen/pages/6555303
 940/Operational+Health+Review+OHR+Meeting+-+Overview>\n\n
