BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Mandatory\n\nApex AscendOS powers the movement and safekeeping 
 of billions of dollars in assets across brokerage\, wealth management\, an
 d workplace investing. Our clients — and the millions of everyday invest
 ors they serve — trust us with their financial lives. That trust is the 
 foundation of everything we do\, and it is ours to protect.\n\nAI is makin
 g us faster and smarter\, but it is also introducing new risks from within
  our own walls — often without realizing it. And as our adversaries adap
 t\, attacks that once required sophistication can now be launched by anyon
 e. Fraudulent emails are now virtually indistinguishable from real ones.\n
 \nIn these 30 minutes\, we'll cover what these threats look like in practi
 ce\, what changes for how you work\, and the specific actions every Apex e
 mployee is responsible for starting now.\n\nAs a reminder\, please follow 
 Zoom best practices: keep your camera on and stay muted unless speaking.\n
 \n________________________________\n\n Apex Calendar SVCS is inviting you 
 to a scheduled Zoom meeting.\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting - - Please note hosts mu
 st use Zoom app or link to start this meeting.\nhttps://apexclearing.zoom.
 us/j/96892019103?from=addon\n\nOne tap mobile\n+13126266799\,\,96892019103
 # US (Chicago)\n+13092053325\,\,96892019103# US\n\nDial by your location\n
